Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}奔向黃昏時分的十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}想見你的心情就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}天空中飄浮的雲朵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}互相碰撞 溶化 消失而去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}也不知從何時開始 我們彼此錯過對方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}即便如此我也會在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}尋求著唯一的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}在藍天畫下了"想見你"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}期盼一直到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}今天也是那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}讓人眩暈 讓人憐愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}猶如向日葵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}和陽光一起競相開放
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}凝望著耀眼的　My Love
